          "class": "DepictionMarkdownView",
          "text": "# Pale\n\nA beautiful and minimalistic UI tweak for iOS.\n\n## Features\n\n- Pale status bar loading support\n\n## Requirements\n\n- Snowboard Status Bar Extension + Juice Status Bar support is required for the LTE icon to work\n- Get Snowboard from https://miro92.com/repo/\n- Does not currently support iOS 15/16\n- Dual SIM users: Need to disable secondary cards\n\n## CallAssist\n\n- 100px perfect support (requires fine-tuning of icon position and size)\n\n## Contains\n\n- Signal\n- Wi-Fi\n- Network Type (3G, 4G, 5G, LTEx2)\n- Battery (Juice)\n\n## Compatibility\n\nSupports iPhone, iPad, and iPod touch running iOS 12.0 to 16.5. Jailbreak required.",
